content_vision: The song is about willpower. Sometimes it's better to do things without planning when you know it's the right thing to do. Sometimes it's better to just stop smoking and drinking coffee, even if you still have both left. You might be curious if you can train your willpower like muscle power. Even if you're good at planning things, there's still no substitute for sheer willpower. It is good to have both planning skills and pure willpower.
